reviewText: This could not be a worse film. Plus the print is almost unwatchable. This film is z-grade in every respect.

First off, this rating is not for the movie, it is for the transfer to dvd, this has to be one of the worst transfers I have ever seen, snap, crackle & pop, lines all through the movie, It is almost unwatchable, I have bought dvd's from Alpha video in the past and they were fine, but this one is a total joke and a total waste of money. Stay away!
